::The soldier's eyes nearly pop out of their sockets, as though he had never before laid eyes on such a curvy ::

::soldier.::

Zhe... zhena? Dugleda da gu prokislo!

::officer.::

Zhe... zhena? I *oficir*!? Dugleda da gu prokislo, bre!

greySoldierArmor
Ej, kud ti zgudnesch prlokpatz? Ne znatnoknem tebigndne schtopschtok.
Eh, komvarische, zdrgachinoslaknrknu sledpo klzno prkuslavcho osch? Oko... ::He takes a look at his watch.:: Sches i satminchetres. Zndrntneche? Da ili ne?
::The soldier stands at attention and salutes you.:: Rad i boj, komvarische oficir. Vam trglasnavno klupsalo, komvarische oficir?
Komvarische, schta s klupoznavego u schtab prekon? Daj da gu trtogzlehnotz razglabasch?
Ej, ej. Komvarische, schta gu rolyatz po magatzin?
::The soldier stands at attention and salutes you.:: Rad i boj, komvarische oficir. Schta oschte u magatzin rolaytzte junkerischkenter brugdzkzna?
::Undo the top button of your uniform.::
::Attack!::

::Salutes you.::
::The soldier stands at attention and salutes you.:: Rad i boj, komvarische oficir.
::[Intimidate] Scowl at him without saying anything.::
Komvarische, schto krznesch u schtab natkretnoskalche? Pa jes' hrknusch brljkoszlgnesch prik! Zguslavaj tvoje mve.
::[Persuade] Cough harshly and make a carrying gesture.::
::[Intimidate] Scowl at him without saying anything.::
::Shrug.::
Ch-chta?
Ti - ti si sagledaschnlk sas balonchad! Razbuna! RAZBUNA!
Komvarische.
Zdrpalno da gu smrdi naglas prokletovagyne gzgne.
Bletko na mudrac ktrknuo golem prodensckan. Saschkrisch.
A?
Zapovaj bre, kturu gdnem ti na schta proletkas.
::[Persuade] Cough harshly and point at your throat.::
::[Persuade] Cough harshly and make a carrying gesture.::
::[Persuade] Cough harshly and point at your throat.::
::Shrug.::
::Shrug again.::
Zplno! Aj s vudregnamo tlepozlniko. Che gu hrngnasch sas Gorko Slimovnknicherga. ::He makes a writing motion with his hand.:: Si trgnavo?
Ah, a schto?
Komvarische?
Sch-schta!? Ti si sagledaschnlk! Trebam chukipay! TREBAM CHUKIPAY!
Ovaj... Drznam, komvarische oficir. ::He lowers his saluting arm and returns to his duty.::

::Stiff as a rail, he blankly stares in front of him. You maintain your scowl for a few moments just to see what will happen. Then, like water running down a stalactite, a drop of sweat emerges from beneath his helmet, slides down his cheek and meets his smoothly shaved jawline. 

And more soon follow...::
::He remains silent, staring blankly in front of himself. You maintain your scowl for a few moments but receive no reaction from the soldier.::
Ja chu ktlnem gruzdevan, komvarische oficir. Samo zguslavajte na hrunkejuszitz.
Komvarische oficir, ja vam moram drguslati rolaytzte drugidaj. Preslem gdugne pogadog.
Kom-komvarisch oficir, vi... ::He briefly hesitates.:: Ovaj, hrslajte. Progledache itoriszoknesch ki uslav. ::He salutes you.:: Rad i boj, komvarische oficir.
Komvarische oficir, ja ne mogu da gu slednikavam na krosle i gudenche. Zslano mi dayte zaguslajte schta oschte u magatzin rolaytzte?
Komvarische oficir?
::Fight!::
Rzazrga ti to ne zplno krumpatzgache. Ti u medichnestvno trebasch da gu desch.
Ej, schta to rabotnisch, bre? Kud zgudnesch prlokpatz, zimtzipzam?
Ih, bre, al ti grlce rzazrga! Schtasch vde u trkorkoborko. Imasch li gu kruslich?
A... ko ti gu poslao na prklomazntzku?
Grlce ti rzazrga da gu trkslovnadno! Ne bre zplno.
Ej, schta to rabotnisch, bre? Daj mu gu zdrnavi kud ti zgudnesch prlokpatz, iliti pznala knuvka?
Komvarish? Schto gduslasch?
::He casts a suspicious eye on you, and soon...:: Ti! Ti nesch irgodnegnohlasch da gi buzderam! Razbuna! TREBAM CHUKIPAY!
Nemo da gu izilitkasch. Kud ti zgudnesch prlokpatz? Ne znatnoknem tebigndne schtopschtok.
::He lowers his saluting arm and returns to his duty.::
::Once the sweat begins drizzling all over his uniform he glances into your eyes, but they deflect his stare like a pair of glaring spotlights.::
Drdnesch mene nemozh, sagledaschnlk zlichi! Razbuna! Razbuna!
Ej bre, zheno, schta grduzlikavisch klplna rtbudalatz? ::He takes a step toward you.::
Zplno. Aj pa grdavaj. Sochijukovnemo sledpo. ::He waves you goodbye.::
Bre! Gorko Slimovnknicherga, s lukovnichnem kilo itrista. Gorku da gu si hrngnaschnio. Si trgnavo sad?
Bre! Schto ti grlce rzazrga! Ne zplno.
A bre, schto bre?
Ali... Zplno chegu. Slavajte na gu gtlno presme kaki neche sluvche da krugnjava. ::He salutes you.:: Rad i boj, komvarische oficir.

::He continues in a serious tone.:: Ali ne trebam klupznovnam ti kuspavno ovde. ::He points toward the stairs.:: Ne slavisch gruzdile hrpave gilomaschkno zlznav. Aj.

::He watches you sternly, waiting for you to leave.::
Zplno, zplno. Nechu kloznim rekozatzkle. Al' kad busch trgnuslomao u magatzinche da gu krslognznorgasch, da gi si prsleo trknogrkche na tuj. Si trgnavo, komvarische? Aj sad...
Medichnestvno da gu desch. Ne bejazavay klompaschnek go uradnivno.
Eto, aj pa grdavaj. Sochijukovnemo sledpo. ::He waves you goodbye.::
::As you walk away you hear the sound of him removing his helmet and wiping the sweat off his face.::

::You drag the young and confused soldier toward you and aim your soft lips toward a collision course with his somewhat dry and cracked ones; the result is an explosion of passion, mostly one-sided.

However, his hand slowly reaches behind your head and finds its way underneath the back of your helmet, and you feel him touching your hair...::
::He waves you goodbye.:: Zplno zslavu.
Zplno zslavu. ::He waves you goodbye.::
Aj u medichnestvno da gu desch. Ti to travnari zdrvnako kuslavi. Bre... ::He waves you goodbye.::
Daj ne kluhdrnaj, komvarische. Schto bre ne valyiadnochesno sas tobom?

::...And yanks it so hard he nearly tears off your entire scalp.::

Ti si zblaknovno miszlela da gu trubnekvnaschisch, a bre? Sagledaschnlk sas balonchad! Razbuna! RAZBUNA!

::You manage to break yourself free of his grasp and prepare for a fight.::
Bre, konachneslo prklezamanzno ihmalo! Ali schto ti grlce rzazrga! Ne zplno.
::He pauses.:: Koj si ti, komvarishe? Zguslavaj thrknoblastimno?
Staj! Ne mrknesch slugovnatrkno plezno! Razbuna! Trebam chukipay vuslavna! CHUKIPAY!
